63
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,359
LA REBELLE

64
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,752
- Bonjour.
- Piper.

65
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,195
- Content de te voir, chérie.
- Moi aussi.

66
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,510
Tu es enceinte.

67
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,796
Oui, on le dirait bien.

68
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,109
Depuis quand ?

69
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:50,750
Tu sais, je voulais t'appeler
pour te l'annoncer, mais bon...

70
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,114
