177
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,559
Nos délires me manquent.

178
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,276
Oui, à moi aussi.

179
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:07,076
Todd. Te voilà, chéri.

180
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,119
Ah, tu es là.

181
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:12,311
